<XMLDocContent PageName="cobalt.graphics.IGraphicsDeviceEnumerator.FilterDevicesNotOfType" Title="FilterDevicesNotOfType method" xmlns="http://www.cobaltrenderer.com/schema/XMLDocSchema.xsd">
  <Paragraph>
    <PageRef PageName="cobalt.graphics.Welcome">Home</PageRef> ->
    <PageRef PageName="cobalt.graphics.IGraphicsDeviceEnumerator">IGraphicsDeviceEnumerator</PageRef> ->
    FilterDevicesNotOfType
  </Paragraph>
  <Section Title="Description">
    <Paragraph>
      The <TypeRef>FilterDevicesNotOfType</TypeRef> method removes all devices which are not of the specified type from the filtered device list.
    </Paragraph>
  </Section>
  <Section Title="Usage">
    <Code Language="C++"><![CDATA[void FilterDevicesNotOfType(IGraphicsDevice::DeviceType type);]]></Code>
    <SubSection Title="Argument list">
      <ArgumentList>
        <ArgumentListEntry Type="IGraphicsDevice::DeviceType" Name="type">
          The device type to remove from the filtered device list.
        </ArgumentListEntry>
      </ArgumentList>
    </SubSection>
  </Section>
